        - content:
            text: |
              <p>صياغة رسالة outreach</p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p><span style="color:#15807A;">✓ نشط</span></p>
      - - content:
            text: |
              <p>Act w/ Approval</p>
        - content:
            text: |
              <p>تنفيذ بعد موافقة</p>
        - content:
            text: |
